title: A Whole New League of Luxury & Close to Everything!
posting_body: ['A whole new league of luxury just entered Plano!', 'Plano has anything and everything within reach.', "With one of the best school districts in the state, plentiful amount of jobs, shopping galore, and so many spectacular restaurants, you'll love calling this area home.", "You're just a 12-minute drive from Downtown Dallas, and walking distance to new local restaurants and bars.", 'The luxe interiors of this apartment include: plush carpeting in the bedrooms, full-sized washer and dryer included, quartz countertops, separate shower with glass enclosure, oversized soaking tub and modern fixtures.', 'The stunning kitchen includes stainless steel appliances with a side-by-side fridge with icemaker, self-cleaning oven, built-in wine rack, ceramic tile backsplash, kitchen island and under counter lighting.', 'This spacious apartment includes expansive closets and pantry with custom shelving, open living space, 9-12 foot ceilings and the option of a pool or courtyard view.', "In addition, if you move-in this month and sign a 12+ month lease, I'll send you a $100 Amazon GIFT CARD after you move-in!", 'All you have to do is put "Desiree with DASH Realty" on your guest card  and leasing application.', 'For more information about this amazing apartment, Call/Text/Email Desiree with DASH Realty today', 'show contact info', '!', 'Mention Ad 733']
